{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "5f9f27e8-f0df-4473-ac14-930707c5b7f3", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/5f9f27e8-f0df-4473-ac14-930707c5b7f3@1.pkg/1772597485402/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597486130", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/5f9f27e8-f0df-4473-ac14-930707c5b7f3@1.pkg/1772597485402/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597486130"}, "identifier": "5f9f27e8-f0df-4473-ac14-930707c5b7f3", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>本题考查传承和弘扬民族精神的表现。</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>①契合活动主题，通过活动学生能深入知晓抗战艰辛历程，传承先辈们不屈不挠等伟大抗战精神；</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>②与抗战胜利主题活动关联不大；</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>③并非此类主题活动的核心目的；</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>④抗战胜利体现了先辈们为国家独立、民族解放的伟大付出，能激发学生爱国热情，明白自身肩负的时代使命。</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>故①④正确，答案选B。</b></span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（原创）2025年是中国人民抗日战争暨世界反法西斯战争胜利80周年，某中学组织&ldquo;铭记抗战岁月&rdquo;主题系列活动，通过参观抗战纪念馆、聆听老兵故事、编排抗战主题情景剧等形式，引导学生（ &nbsp; ）</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>①了解抗战历史，传承抗战精神</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>②增强环保意识，践行绿色生活</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justif